snippet.title: Fall of Porcupine - Official Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Take another look at Fall of Porcupine, including gameplay, and some of the characters, in this trailer for the upcoming story adventure game. Fall of Porcupine will be available on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, Nintendo Switch, and PC on June 15, 2023. Fall of Porcupine explores the collision of work and daily life – an exciting reflection of an unhealthy healthcare system. Experience the story of Finley and his friends and uncover the darkest secrets of Porcupine and its residents.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
